For a breif moment, a low growl escaped the chrome male.  The emotion in his optics mirrored his namesake.  a breif glimpse of the viral anger manifested, his instability showing his true unpredictable nature.  His firm grip instantly became vise like, his face twisted into a hellish glare.  But the moment passed and he let her go, and stepped back, stuggling to regain control.  After a moment of inner battle, he calmed.

&quot;That is why... at any given moment I can snap.  It is nothing against you, but you would not be prepared to face me.  You fell in love with the calm and sincere Malice, you have no idea what I can do when I am not so nice and sincere.  It is for your safety.  I am no saint.  I have killed in most cruel ways, I may not be much better than Unicron.  But I want you to be safe, that is why you must keep your distance from me.  Wolfblade understands the risks better, and I would not be able to hurt her as easily.  I will tell you what I will tell her.  Stay away from me when I am angry or going to fight.  It is not safe for anyone.  I still love you, but it must be...&quot;

He took a step back.

&quot;From a distance.  You can find another to hold close in my place, love is notoriously fickle.&quot;

